" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF67pUgO.jpg&h=4248c635&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afd04b991be80c6baa6173162ad498e02f627a6d","tid":1726788,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:37:40.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"75d39fb7e7c09241ca99b825323387f267e74266","tid":1726788,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:42:51.000Z","msg":"他們在打的是「<strong>中共政權保衛戰</strong>」，而你們僅僅是在打「<strong>香港生活方式保衛戰</strong>」<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，第一就是分化，把勇武派、和理非派拆分，第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能，坦白說，還是太嫩。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是北京要製造的焦點轉移。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂。</span>"},{"pid":"ddd86f7224ab7f0f79e44ed14ec8ed2065c3f06c","tid":1726788,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T07:20:45.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"6ab9ff104c610bfe1a525460db01f5c43bf814df","tid":1726788,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T07:21:25.000Z","msg":"Pushp"},{"pid":"459af2c62e19f919a2f9c98193f299bbff729d89","tid":1726788,"uid":76078,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf2e96113d93075b774246f27858aed